Python program to find the sum of the series: 1! +2! +3! +4! +5! â€¦. till the given number N. 

n=int(input("Enter the value of N: "))
sumn=0
for i in range(1,n+1):
    factorial=1
    for j in range(1, i+1):
        factorial *= j
        sumn += factorial
print(f"The sum fo the series 1! + 2! + 3!+ .... + {n} is: {sumn}")
